  <thing-type id="erone_hmlm001_00_000" listed="false">
    <label>HM-LM001 Lighting Module</label>
    <description>Lighting Module&lt;br /&gt&lt;h1&gtOverview&lt;/h1&gt&lt;ul&gt&lt;li&gtUse with incandescent light bulbs up to 200W&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtControl on/off for attached lamp&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtDim the attached lamp&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtLED shows that module is working&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtManual override button&lt;/li&gt &lt;/ul&gt&lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtInclusion Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;ul&gt&lt;li&gtStart the inclusion process on the hub&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtSingle click the button on the device&lt;/li&gt &lt;/ul&gt&lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtExclusion Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;ul&gt&lt;li&gtStart the exclusion process on the hub&lt;/li&gt &lt;li&gtTriple click the button on the device&lt;/li&gt &lt;/ul&gt</description>
